<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Activities — Line Engine</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design.css">
</head>
<body>
{{> _nav }}

<div class="swe-container" style="padding-top: var(--space-xxl); padding-bottom: var(--space-section);">

    <div class="swe-flex-between swe-mb-xl">
        <div>
            <h1 class="swe-display-lg" style="margin: 0;">Activity Catalog</h1>
            <p class="swe-body-md swe-mute" style="margin: var(--space-sm) 0 0;">
                등록된 <code>@Activity</code> 메타데이터 — DAG 노드의 <code>activityNm</code>으로 사용
            </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/api/workflow/activities" class="swe-btn-tertiary" target="_blank">JSON API</a>
    </div>

    <div class="swe-grid swe-grid-3 swe-mb-xl">
        <div class="swe-stat-card">
            <div class="swe-stat-label">Total</div>
            <div class="swe-stat-value">{{totalCount}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{#entries}}
    <div class="swe-card swe-mb-xl">
        <div class="swe-flex-between">
            <div>
                <div class="swe-heading-md" style="margin: 0;">
                    <code style="background: var(--surface-card); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: var(--radius-xs); font-size: 18px;">{{activityName}}</code>
                </div>
                <div class="swe-caption swe-mute" style="margin-top: var(--space-xs);">
                    {{beanClass}}.<strong style="color: var(--body);">{{methodName}}</strong>()
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swe-row">
                <span class="swe-keycap">retry: {{retryCount}}</span>
                <span class="swe-keycap">backoff: {{backoffSeconds}}s</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: var(--space-lg); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; gap: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);">
            <div class="swe-caption swe-mute">Parameters</div>
            <div>
                {{#parameterTypes}}
                <code style="background: var(--surface-card); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: var(--radius-xs); font-size: 12px; margin-right: var(--space-xs);">{{.}}</code>
                {{/parameterTypes}}
                {{^parameterTypes}}<span class="swe-mute">—</span>{{/parameterTypes}}
            </div>
            <div class="swe-caption swe-mute">Returns</div>
            <div>
                <code style="background: var(--surface-card); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: var(--radius-xs); font-size: 12px;">{{returnType}}</code>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{/entries}}

    {{^entries}}
    <div class="swe-card" style="text-align: center; color: var(--mute); padding: var(--space-section);">
        No activities registered. <code>@Activity</code> 어노테이션이 붙은 컴포넌트를 추가하세요.
    </div>
    {{/entries}}

</div>
</body>
</html>
